Package org.friendsbalt.javaIntro

Class StrictGrid

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.friendsbalt.javaIntro.Grid
      • org.friendsbalt.javaIntro.StrictGrid
  • public abstract class StrictGrid
extends Grid
    A StrictGrid is one in which items in the grid are aligned to the grid strictly . That is, an object can only have a location exactly in the center of each grid square and cannot move "through" the grid.
